translation.en: Everyone, be careful. We're almost there.
translation.zh: 大家小心 我们快到了

translation.en: Lord, when I said, "Cross my heart and hope to die young and pretty,"
translation.zh: 主 当我发誓 希望死时保持年轻漂亮

translation.en: I did not mean today!
translation.zh: 我不是说今天

translation.en: Ray Ray, stop being so dramatic.
translation.zh: 瑞瑞 别这么夸张

translation.en: I'm not going to stop being me right before I die!
translation.zh: 除非我死了 否则我就是这样

translation.en: No one is going to die-- [screams]
translation.zh: 没人会死

translation.en: Amber, don't fall. I got us a Groupon for a couple's massage.
translation.zh: 安博 别掉下去 我买了情侣按摩优惠套票

translation.en: I'd rather plummet to my death.
translation.zh: 我宁愿摔死

translation.en: [screams] I'm slipping! Hold on!
translation.zh: -我抓不住了 -坚持住

translation.en: [Amber grunts] Kaylie!
translation.zh: 凯莉

translation.en: [paparazzi shouting] Kaylie!
translation.zh: 凯莉

translation.en: Order!
translation.zh: 肃静

translation.en: Ooh, I'd love a sparkling water with a slice of cucumber. Thank you!
translation.zh: 我要加黄瓜片的苏打水 谢谢

translation.en: The defendant,
translation.zh: 被告

translation.en: Kaylee Konrad,
translation.zh: 凯莉·康纳德

translation.en: gunned her Mercedes through a Dolce & Gabbana display window,
translation.zh: 驾驶其奔驰车辆冲入店铺

translation.en: committing aggravated assault
translation.zh: 对一些人体模特

translation.en: on a bunch of really surprised mannequins.
translation.zh: 进行了严重的人身攻击

translation.en: It was an accident.
translation.zh: 那是意外

translation.en: Sorry, guys.
translation.zh: 抱歉了 各位

translation.en: Besides, mock turtlenecks, that's the real crime.
translation.zh: 而且那些高领衣服才真的是犯罪

translation.en: -[gavel banging] -Order! And I said no cameras.
translation.zh: 肃静 不准拍照

translation.en: Just be quiet and look pretty.
translation.zh: 你安静点 装可爱 你的嘴唇看起来很薄

translation.en: BTW, your lips look thin. I told you to plump.
translation.zh: 你安静点 装可爱 你的嘴唇看起来很薄 我叫你丰满点

translation.en: Miss Konrad, do you have anything you'd like to say?
translation.zh: 康纳德小姐 你有什么要说的吗？

translation.en: Yes, Your Honor. [clears throat]
translation.zh: 是的 法官大人

translation.en: I believe our justice system needs to stop persecuting innocent celebrities
translation.zh: 我希望司法体系不要迫害无辜的名人

translation.en: and start paying more attention to what's happening in our communities.
translation.zh: 应更多地关注我们社区发生的事

translation.en: I rest my briefcase.
translation.zh: 我说完了

translation.en: -[gavel bangs] -[Judge] Order.
translation.zh: 肃静

translation.en: You're not innocent, and I should send you to jail.
translation.zh: 你并不无辜 我应该送你进监狱

translation.en: No! She could never handle that.
translation.zh: 不 -她绝对做不到 -我可以

translation.en: I could so.
translation.zh: -她绝对做不到 -我可以

translation.en: Please! You once had to ride in the back of a non-stretch limo,
translation.zh: 拜托 你有次坐在豪车后座

translation.en: and you broke out in hives.
translation.zh: 你爆发了荨麻疹

translation.en: It had faux leather seats!
translation.zh: 那是人造皮的座椅

translation.en: I'm lucky to be alive.
translation.zh: 我能活着就不错了

translation.en: Although, ratings could go through the roof.
translation.zh: 可能收视率会创新高

translation.en: [gasps] We could make a fortune on the Kaylie Dream Cell.
translation.zh: 凯莉的梦幻牢房是个赚钱的主意

translation.en: Shiv sold separately.
translation.zh: 还能卖自制武器

translation.en: I'd buy that.
translation.zh: 我会买的

translation.en: Miss Konrad, since you mentioned community,
translation.zh: 肃静 康纳德小姐 既然你刚才提及社区 我判你进行

translation.en: I hereby sentence you to one year of community service.
translation.zh: 既然你刚才提及社区 我判你进行 一年的社区服务

translation.en: That is so sweet! The community's gonna work for me for a whole year?
translation.zh: 太棒了 社区要为我服务一年吗？

translation.en: ♪ Team Kaylie, ay, ay Team Kaylie ♪
translation.zh: 凯莉小分队 哎 哎 凯莉小分队

translation.en: ♪ Where's a map? 'Cuz I could use directions ♪
translation.zh: 哪里有地图 我要看看

translation.en: ♪ To get from Hollywood to firewood ♪
translation.zh: 怎么从好莱坞到木柴道

translation.en: ♪ Even though I don't know Where I'm headin' ♪
translation.zh: 就算我不知道要去哪里

translation.en: ♪ I'm making friends and looking good ♪
translation.zh: 我要广交朋友 容光焕发

translation.en: ♪ We may not belong But who cares? Bring it on ♪
translation.zh: 可能有点出格 但谁在意呢 尽管来吧

translation.en: ♪ 'Cuz I know we're gonna find our way ♪
translation.zh: 我们终会找到自己的方式

translation.en: ♪ Team Kaylie ♪
translation.zh: 凯莉小分队 当你的生活变得疯狂

translation.en: ♪ When your life gets wild Follow me through the wilderness ♪
translation.zh: 凯莉小分队 当你的生活变得疯狂 跟随我穿过荒野

translation.en: ♪ Team Kaylie ♪
translation.zh: 凯莉小分队 苦中作乐

translation.en: ♪ Roughing it in style Together, yeah, we'll be killin' it ♪
translation.zh: 凯莉小分队 苦中作乐 团结一致 我们无所不能

translation.en: ♪ Team Kaylie, ay, ay Team Kaylie ♪
translation.zh: 凯莉小分队 哎 哎 凯莉小分队

translation.en: -Okay, how does that look? -Perfect.
translation.zh: （比科露营俱乐部） -好了 看起来如何？ -完美

translation.en: Perfect would be you and me in the cafeteria
translation.zh: 完美应该是你和我在餐厅里

translation.en: Lady and the Tramp-ing a strand of spaghetti.
translation.zh: 一起享用同一份意粉

translation.en: I've got an in with the lunch lady.
translation.zh: 我和午餐小姐能梦想成真

translation.en: And I still have a thumb tack.
translation.zh: 我这还有一个图钉

translation.en: So... rain check?
translation.zh: 那还是改天吧

translation.en: [Chewy] Ow!
translation.zh: 啊

translation.en: Silence!
translation.zh: 安静

translation.en: Valeria, what are you doing back there?
translation.zh: 瓦莱莉雅 你在那边做什么？

translation.en: Putting a Santeria curse on Mr. Jabowski.
translation.zh: 对查保斯基老师下圣特里亚诅咒

translation.en: [chuckles] That's the last time he gives me detention.
translation.zh: 那是最后一次他让我留堂

translation.en: This deadly curse will follow Mr. Jabowski and his children's children's children
translation.zh: 这个致命诅咒将跟随查保斯基老师 还有他孩子的孩子的孩子

translation.en: until the end of time!
translation.zh: 直到永恒

translation.en: And if that doesn't work, these shells are super sharp,
translation.zh: 如果这没用的话 这些贝壳很锋利

translation.en: and I left one on his chair.
translation.zh: 我会放一个在他椅子上

translation.en: Wow, this turnout is lamer than the Spice Girls reunion tour.
translation.zh: 哇 参加人数比辣妹组合的 团聚巡演更可怜

translation.en: Baby Spice pushing 50? That's just sad.
translation.zh: 婴儿辣妹也快50岁了 真让人伤感

translation.en: Ray Ray!
translation.zh: 瑞瑞

translation.en: Did you come to your senses and decide to join our Wilderness Club?
translation.zh: 你终于想清楚要加入露营俱乐部吗？

translation.en: Baby girl, we've been over this.
translation.zh: 宝贝 我们以前就讨论过 我搭配什么都很好看

translation.en: I look good in everything, except dirt, and culottes.
translation.zh: 宝贝 我们以前就讨论过 我搭配什么都很好看 除了泥土和裙裤

translation.en: I have got to work on my calves.
translation.zh: 我要锻炼小腿

translation.en: But the kickoff hike to Sunset Peak is today!
translation.zh: 但徒步去日落峰是今天

translation.en: Ten teams from our school district compete,
translation.zh: 我们校区有十支队伍参与角逐

translation.en: and whoever plants their flag at the top first gets a Silver Pine Cone!
translation.zh: 谁能先将旗帜插在山顶的 可以获得银松果奖

translation.en: You lost me at hike.
translation.zh: 徒步时你把我搞丢了

translation.en: You know we've been tight since we were in diapers.
translation.zh: 你知道我们青梅竹马感情很好

translation.en: Mine were stylish. Yours were just... full.
translation.zh: 我很时尚 而你只是刚刚满

translation.en: But when it comes to Mother Nature, Ray Ray is JOMO.
translation.zh: 对于大自然 瑞瑞觉得错过也挺好的

translation.en: But we need all the help we can get!
translation.zh: 但我们需要尽可能多的帮助

translation.en: I do not want to lose again to those spoiled, snotty Lumberjacks.
translation.zh: 我不想再输给那个娇气 幼稚的伐木工队

translation.en: May they choke on their filthy money 'til their blood-soaked eyeballs burst
translation.zh: 让他们被肮脏的钱呛死 浸满鲜血的眼球

translation.en: from their skulls!
translation.zh: 从头骨中爆射而出

translation.en: Which is exactly what happened last year
translation.zh: 这就像是去年哥斯顿比老师在溜索上

translation.en: when Miss Gerstonblatt had a stroke on the zipline.
translation.zh: 这就像是去年哥斯顿比老师在溜索上 中风的那个样子

translation.en: And now we don't have an adult to lead our Wilderness Club.
translation.zh: 所以我们的露营俱乐部 没有成年领队了

translation.en: We don't need an adult.
translation.zh: 我们不需要领队

translation.en: My mom and I used to go camping all the time, so I can lead us to victory.
translation.zh: 我妈和我经常去露营 我可以带领我们获得胜利

translation.en: But the rules say we need an adult.
translation.zh: 但规则要求我们有个成年领队

translation.en: Screw the rules.
translation.zh: 让规则去死

translation.en: But rules lead to order, and order leads to lists, and lists lead to happiness.
translation.zh: 有规则才有秩序 才有清单 最终才有幸福

translation.en: Besides, no one at the school ever wants the job anyway.
translation.zh: 但是在学校里没人想当领队

translation.en: Especially after Miss Gerstonblatt took that zipline to heaven.
translation.zh: 尤其是哥斯顿比老师从溜索 直接到天堂后

translation.en: And you think some stranger is just going to walk through that door
translation.zh: 你以为会有陌生人走进门

translation.en: and say, "Let me lead you"?
translation.zh: 然后说 让我来做领队

translation.en: Let me lead you.
translation.zh: 让我来做领队

translation.en: Oh! Hello.
translation.zh: 噢 你们好

translation.en: -OMG, that's Kaylie Konrad! -Who cares?
translation.zh: -我的天 那是凯莉·康纳德 -那又怎样？

translation.en: Everyone!
translation.zh: 各位

translation.en: See? I'm a do-gooder.
translation.zh: 看到吗？我热心公益

translation.en: Kaylie Konrad picks up trash!
translation.zh: 凯莉·康纳德捡垃圾

translation.en: That was my lunch!
translation.zh: 那是我的午餐

translation.en: Kaylie Konrad helps homeless children.
translation.zh: 凯莉·康纳德帮助街头儿童

translation.en: I'm not homeless.
translation.zh: 我不是街头儿童

translation.en: Oh. Awkward.
translation.zh: 噢 尴尬了

translation.en: I curse you.
translation.zh: 我诅咒你

translation.en: Okay, we're done. Remember, I'll be at NOBU tonight.
translation.zh: 好了 就这样吧 记得我今晚会在诺布

translation.en: I have to meet Kaylie. What do I do?
translation.zh: 我要和凯莉打招呼 我该做什么？

translation.en: Just stay cool.
translation.zh: 保持冷静

translation.en: Right. Cool.
translation.zh: 对的 冷静

translation.en: I love you, Kaylie Konrad! Can I touch you?
translation.zh: 我爱你 凯莉·康纳德 能摸你吗？

translation.en: [giggles] I touched her!
translation.zh: 我摸到了

translation.en: You do know what cool means, right?
translation.zh: 你知道冷静什么意思吗？

translation.en: Excuse me, Miss Konrad, what are you doing at Pico Middle School?
translation.zh: 不好意思 康纳德小姐 你来我们学校做什么？

translation.en: And you should be wearing a visitor's pass.
translation.zh: 你应该戴着访客证件

translation.en: I just reprimanded Kaylie Konrad!
translation.zh: 我刚训斥了凯莉·康纳德

translation.en: Your principal sent me to this room to help you guys out with some club.
translation.zh: 你们校长叫我来这里 帮你们搞什么俱乐部

translation.en: So, where's the VIP area?
translation.zh: 贵宾区在哪里？

translation.en: Oh, no way!
translation.zh: 不行

translation.en: You come with me.
translation.zh: 你跟我来

translation.en: You're the smallest bouncer I've ever seen.
translation.zh: 哇 你是我见过最小的门卫

translation.en: Principal Dana, I need a different do-gooder thingy.
translation.zh: 德纳校长 我想要其他的服务项目

translation.en: This tiny bouncer here says that we might have to walk through dirt.
translation.zh: 这个门卫说我们可能要满身泥泞

translation.en: Yeah, I do not see myself doing that.
translation.zh: 是的 我不认为我能这样做

translation.en: Well, I did not see myself scoping Tinder every night
translation.zh: 我也不能每晚吃着冷混沌 一边浏览交友软件

translation.en: eating cold ravioli out of a can, but... here we are.
translation.zh: 我也不能每晚吃着冷混沌 一边浏览交友软件 但现实就是这样

translation.en: Aw, you're so lucky you can Tinder. I'm way too famous.
translation.zh: 你能用交友软件真好 我太有名了

translation.en: And TBH, you might do better on Silver Singles.
translation.zh: 老实说 你应该更多考虑 50岁以上的组别

translation.en: On there, you're like a seven, minimum!
translation.zh: 在那里你至少会有7分

translation.en: Principal Dana, we don't need an adult, especially not her!
translation.zh: 德纳校长 我们不要成年领队 尤其是她

translation.en: I have tons of wilderness experience, so I should be the leader.
translation.zh: 我有很多野外经验 我可以做领队

translation.en: And I should be in Paris.
translation.zh: 我也应该在巴黎

translation.en: I'm missing Fashion Week, and it's missing moi.
translation.zh: 我要错过时装周了 我不应缺席

translation.en: Okay, I feel for you both as much as my pain medication will let me, but...
translation.zh: 好了 我已经尽可能理解你们

translation.en: the judge sent Kaylie to me, I sent her to you, and that's that.
translation.zh: 法官将凯莉送来 我将她派给你 就这么简单

translation.en: Did that sound commanding? I've been practicing in front of my cats.
translation.zh: 听起来是不是很有威严？ 我在我的猫面前练习过

translation.en: -[both] But-- -All right, fine. You win.
translation.zh: -但是… -好了 你赢了

translation.en: All right, Amber, you can lead a bunch of teenagers into the woods unsupervised,
translation.zh: 安博 你可以在没领队的情况下 带着一帮青少年进入森林

translation.en: -and Kaylie you can go to Paris. -[both] Really?
translation.zh: -凯莉也可以去巴黎 -真的吗？

translation.en: No!
translation.zh: 不可能

translation.en: Apparently, I need to work on my sarcasm in front of my cats too.
translation.zh: 看来我也要在我的猫面前练习反讽

translation.en: Principal Dana, even if we do need an adult,
translation.zh: 德纳校长 就算我们真的需要 一个成年领队

translation.en: do you really think Kaylie Konrad is the best choice?
translation.zh: 德纳校长 就算我们真的需要 一个成年领队 你觉得凯莉·康纳德合适吗？

translation.en: This is the girl that cried on her reality show
translation.zh: 这个女孩在真人秀上哭泣

translation.en: when her car got bird poop on it.
translation.zh: 因为她的车上有鸟粪

translation.en: [crying] No! No!
translation.zh: 不！

translation.en: Not my car!
translation.zh: 不要在我的车上

translation.en: Okay, to be fair, that bird had some serious stomach issues.
translation.zh: 好吧 我真的觉得那只鸟 有严重的胃病

translation.en: You look stupid.
translation.zh: 你看起来很傻

translation.en: All I'm saying is I wanna beat the Lumberjacks this year,
translation.zh: 我想说 我今年想打败伐木工队

translation.en: which is going to be really tough, and Kaylie Konrad could never handle that.
translation.zh: 这过程会很艰难 凯莉·康纳德没法应付

translation.en: [Kit] Kaylie could never handle that.
translation.zh: 凯莉绝对做不到

translation.en: Wait. You don't think I can do it?
translation.zh: 等等 你觉得我做不到？

translation.en: Nobody does!
translation.zh: 没人能做到

translation.en: I mean, if you last longer than a week, I owe the judge a dinner at Sizzler.
translation.zh: 我是说 如果你能坚持超过一周 我就要请法官吃牛扒

translation.en: Well, you're wrong, and I'll prove it.
translation.zh: 你错了 我会证明的

translation.en: Ooh, can you prove it somewhere else? I just got a message from OkCupid.
translation.zh: 你能去别的地方证明吗？ 我刚收到交友信息

translation.en: Oh! [giggles]
translation.zh: 噢

translation.en: Apparently, a Nigerian prince wants to meet me.
translation.zh: 看起来一个尼日利亚的王子想见我

translation.en: This could be my last chance at happiness.
translation.zh: 这可能是我获得幸福的最后机会

translation.en: Okay, now I just need to send him my bank account information.
translation.zh: 好了 现在我只需要将 银行账号信息发过去

translation.en: -But Principal Dana-- -Ah.
translation.zh: -但是德纳校长… -啊

translation.en: It's Princess Dana to you.
translation.zh: 叫我德纳公主

translation.en: Off you go.
translation.zh: 你们走吧

translation.en: Greetings,
translation.zh: 你好

translation.en: my Nigerian subjects.
translation.zh: 我的尼日利亚臣民

translation.en: Remember, everything the light touches is mine.
translation.zh: 记得 普天之下 莫非王土

translation.en: All right, kids, to the wilderness!
translation.zh: 好了 孩子们 我们去露营了

translation.en: -The door is that way. -The door is that way!
translation.zh: -门在那边 -门在那边

translation.en: Wait for Ray Ray!
translation.zh: 要等等瑞瑞

translation.en: Had to get my wilderness look on point.
translation.zh: 我必须有完美的野外造型

translation.en: I thought dirt wasn't your color?
translation.zh: 我以为泥土跟你不配？

translation.en: Turns out, I go with everything.
translation.zh: 其实我跟所有东西都能配

translation.en: So can I go with you? Please, please, please!
translation.zh: 我能和你一起去吗？拜托了

translation.en: Okay, just no more touching my hair.
translation.zh: 好吧 只是别再摸我头发

translation.en: I promise. Cross my heart and hope to die young and pretty.
translation.zh: 我保证 我发誓 我希望死时保持年轻漂亮

translation.en: Okay. Let's see here.
translation.zh: 好了 我们来看看

translation.en: Uh, Miss Konrad, that's a star map of celebrity homes.
translation.zh: 康纳德小姐 这是显示名人居所的 追星地图

translation.en: Oh, I know.
translation.zh: 噢 我知道

translation.en: I just wanted to show you that my house is bigger than Gigi Hadid's. Yay!
translation.zh: 我只是想告诉你们 我的房子比吉吉·哈蒂德的更大

translation.en: Yay!
translation.zh: 好啊

translation.en: I know which way to go.
translation.zh: 我知道该怎么走

translation.en: We head north to get to Sunset Peak where we plant our flag,
translation.zh: 我们往北走去日落峰 我们要在那里插旗

translation.en: which is... this way.
translation.zh: 我们往北走去日落峰 我们要在那里插旗 -是这边 -噢

translation.en: Aw! Is that a picture of you and your mom?
translation.zh: -是这边 -噢 这是你和你妈的照片吗？

translation.en: That's so sweet.
translation.zh: 真是亲密

translation.en: She doesn't look like she's judging you.
translation.zh: 她看起来不会挑剔你

translation.en: We have to hurry.
translation.zh: 我们要快点

translation.en: -Wait. I don't have a signal. -Kaylie needs a signal!
translation.zh: -等等 没信号了 -凯莉需要信号

translation.en: Stars, they're just like us.
translation.zh: 星星 看起来就像我们

translation.en: There's no cell service in the woods.
translation.zh: 树林里没有手机信号

translation.en: [sighs] Fine. I'll use the Wi-Fi.
translation.zh: 好吧 我用无线网络

translation.en: What's the password?
translation.zh: 密码是什么？

translation.en: We're going to die out here.
translation.zh: 我们会死在这里

translation.en: Is that all lowercase?
translation.zh: 都是小写的吗？

translation.en: [sighs] Let's go! We have to beat the Lumberjacks to the peak!
translation.zh: 走吧 我们要打败伐木工队

translation.en: In your dreams, Porcupukes!
translation.zh: 做梦吧 豪猪队

translation.en: Emphasis on the "poor."
translation.zh: 加上“可怜兮兮的”

translation.en: Drop dead, Lumberjerks.
translation.zh: 去死吧 伐木工

translation.en: Emphasis on "drop dead."
translation.zh: 加上“死翘翘的”

translation.en: I curse the Lumberjerks!
translation.zh: 我要诅咒你们伐木工

translation.en: I think someone already has. How else can you explain those outfits?
translation.zh: 我想他们已经被诅咒了 不然怎么解释那些着装？

translation.en: May your blisters get blisters until your shoes are drenched in blood!
translation.zh: 愿你的水泡越来越大 直到你的鞋子被血浸透

translation.en: Yeah, that happened to me once at a photoshoot for Manolo Blahnik.
translation.zh: 我为马诺洛·布拉尼克拍照时 试过一次

translation.en: Twelve straight hours in six-inch stilettos...
translation.zh: 穿着6寸细高跟鞋连续站了12小时

translation.en: I still can't get my heels down.
translation.zh: 我还不能脱掉鞋子

translation.en: Kaylie Konrad? What are you doing with these lames?
translation.zh: 凯莉·康纳德？ 你为何和这些无用鬼在一起？

translation.en: I'm the leader of the lames!
translation.zh: 我是这帮家伙的领队

translation.en: No, she's not.
translation.zh: 不 她不是

translation.en: We're her punishment.
translation.zh: 我们是她受罚的代价

translation.en: She's ours.
translation.zh: 她是我们的

translation.en: Who cares? We're gonna beat you like a baby seal!
translation.zh: 谁管你 我们会将你们踩在脚底

translation.en: And win that annual Wilderness Trophy, just like last year.
translation.zh: 像去年一样赢得年度荒野奖杯

translation.en: [man] Afternoon, y'all.
translation.zh: 下午好 各位

translation.en: Wow. You're like a real-life pickup truck commercial.
translation.zh: 哇 你就像是真人皮卡车广告

translation.en: I'm Colt Axelrod, new volunteer leader of the Lumberjacks.
translation.zh: 我是柯尔特·艾克斯罗德 伐木工队的领队

translation.en: Sorry, no autographs.
translation.zh: 抱歉 没有签名

translation.en: It's not fair to the kids.
translation.zh: 这对孩子不公平

translation.en: Uh, excuse me. Am I supposed to know who you are?
translation.zh: 不好意思 你是不是名人？

translation.en: Yes.
translation.zh: 是的

translation.en: This is Kaylie Konrad, as in the Konrad Kronicles,
translation.zh: 这是凯莉·康纳德 《凯莉粉丝团》的主角

translation.en: biggest reality TV show ever.
translation.zh: 史无前例的真人秀节目

translation.en: I don't own a TV.
translation.zh: 我没有电视

translation.en: I'd rather hike, or fish, or read.
translation.zh: 我喜欢徒步 钓鱼和看书

translation.en: Oh, you mean like on a Kindle?
translation.zh: 你是说电子书吗？

translation.en: Uh, no, a book. [chuckles] It's like a Kindle...
translation.zh: 不是 普通书 就像是看豆

translation.en: but it's a book.
translation.zh: 但是 是纸质的

translation.en: I think people spend way too much time on their devices
translation.zh: 我觉得人们花太多时间在电子设备上

translation.en: and all that social media nonsense.
translation.zh: 还有社交媒体的垃圾新闻

translation.en: [scoffs] Nonsense? That nonsense paid for my private island
translation.zh: 垃圾新闻？但垃圾新闻帮我 赚够钱买私人岛屿

translation.en: where all the money has my face on it.
translation.zh: 岛上货币印着我的样子

translation.en: Twenty Kaylies buys a lobster dinner.
translation.zh: 20凯莉币可以吃龙虾大餐

translation.en: Well, hey, as I've tried to tell these kids, money can't buy you happiness.
translation.zh: 我一直跟孩子们说 钱没法买到快乐

translation.en: Well, clearly you've never jet skied off a mega-yacht.
translation.zh: 很明显你没有在豪华游艇上 玩过水上摩托

translation.en: No, but I once jumped off a kayak to save a wounded beaver.
translation.zh: 没有 但我试过从皮艇上跳下 救一只受伤的海狸

translation.en: I named him Bucky.
translation.zh: 我帮他起名叫巴奇

translation.en: Let's go!
translation.zh: 我们走吧

translation.en: Let's go! Let's go! Let's go!
translation.zh: 走吧

translation.en: Hold on.
translation.zh: 等等

translation.en: No way can we compete with them. Did you see their calves?
translation.zh: 我们绝对没法胜过他们 你看到他们的小腿吗？

translation.en: Well, if we can't catch them, might as well just give up and go home.
translation.zh: 既然我们追不上 我们还是放弃回家吧

translation.en: You had me at "give up."
translation.zh: 放弃打动了我

translation.en: Don't give up.
translation.zh: 别放弃

translation.en: May the best team win.
translation.zh: 还是志在参与

translation.en: We Porcupines do not give up!
translation.zh: 我们豪猪队不能放弃

translation.en: We're proud, prickly, and persistent! Now let's run!
translation.zh: 我们骄傲 不屈服 执着！我们快点跑

translation.en: Easy for you to say. Your heels still touch the ground.
translation.zh: 你说就容易 而且你还站着

translation.en: Why don't we just take that shortcut?
translation.zh: 我们怎么不走捷径？

translation.en: I don't think that's a good idea.
translation.zh: 我觉得这样不好

translation.en: Yeah, we're supposed to stick to the trail.
translation.zh: 我们应该按路线走

translation.en: [scoffs] Says who?
translation.zh: 谁说的？

translation.en: Literally everyone.
translation.zh: 所有人

translation.en: Okay, are you gonna listen to a bunch of signs
translation.zh: 好吧 你是要听从这里的指示牌

translation.en: that were placed here with a lot of careful thought and planning,
translation.zh: 好吧 你是要听从这里的指示牌 可能有各种小心考虑因素 还是听我说？

translation.en: or are you gonna listen to me?
translation.zh: 可能有各种小心考虑因素 还是听我说？

translation.en: And before you answer, may I remind you that I won a People's Choice Award.
translation.zh: 在你回答之前 我提醒你 我赢过民众选择奖

translation.en: It's your only shot at winning. No offense to your cool blister curse.
translation.zh: 你要赢只有这个机会 不是针对你的水泡诅咒

translation.en: None taken. BTW, have you noticed any warts popping up on you?
translation.zh: 没事 话说你有否注意到 自己身上有疣出现？

translation.en: Ew, no.
translation.zh: 呃 没有

translation.en: Why?
translation.zh: 为什么问？

translation.en: No reason.
translation.zh: 没事

translation.en: Well, since we'll never catch them on the trail,
translation.zh: 既然走他们的路线没法赶超

translation.en: I guess we have to try it your way.
translation.zh: 我们只能试试你的路线了

translation.en: Yay, I'm a leader! Follow me!
translation.zh: 好啊 我是领队 跟我来

translation.en: I knew I'd be walking through dirt.
translation.zh: 我就知道我会满身泥泞

translation.en: Didn't know I'd be eating it.
translation.zh: 但我没想到还会吃土

translation.en: Watch your step. It's slippery.
translation.zh: 小心脚步 很滑的

translation.en: We're not gonna make it! Kaylie, can I please be buried with you?
translation.zh: 我们做不到的 凯莉 我死了你将我和你合葬

translation.en: No, because when I die, my mom wants me cremated so she can use my ashes
translation.zh: 不会的 如果我死了 我妈会将我火化 这样她就能卖我的骨灰

translation.en: to sell limited edition genuine platinum-plated necklaces.
translation.zh: 限量版纯正镀铂项链

translation.en: Whoa! That's cold.
translation.zh: 哇 那很冷酷

translation.en: No, it's not! She promised to give me half the profits.
translation.zh: 不 没有 她答应给我一半收益

translation.en: But... you'll be dead.
translation.zh: 但你都死了

translation.en: Oh.
translation.zh: 噢

translation.en: Then I want 100% of the profits!
translation.zh: 那我应该要全部收益

translation.en: That'll show her.
translation.zh: 她也不是省油的灯

translation.en: Lord, when I said, "Cross my heart and hope to die young and pretty,"
translation.zh: 主 当我发誓 希望死时保持年轻漂亮

translation.en: I did not mean today!
translation.zh: 我不是说今天

translation.en: No one is going to die-- [screams]
translation.zh: 没人会死

translation.en: Amber, don't fall! I got us a Groupon for a couple's massage.
translation.zh: 安博 别掉下去 我买了情侣按摩优惠套票

translation.en: I'd rather plummet to my death.
translation.zh: 我宁愿摔死

translation.en: [screams] I'm slipping! Hold on!
translation.zh: -我抓不住了 -坚持住

translation.en: [grunts] Kaylie!
translation.zh: 凯莉

translation.en: I'll get you.
translation.zh: 我会抓住你

translation.en: Ah! I see a foothold.
translation.zh: 我看到个落脚点

translation.en: That's more like a toehold!
translation.zh: 那地方只能落脚趾

translation.en: That's all I need. Thank you, Manolo Blahnik!
translation.zh: 那就够了 谢谢 马诺洛·布拉尼克

translation.en: Amber, grab my hand.
translation.zh: 安博 抓住我的手

translation.en: -I can't. I'll fall! -[Kaylie] No, you won't!
translation.zh: -不行 我会掉下去 -你不会的

translation.en: There's a toehold near your right foot. Feel for it,
translation.zh: 在你右脚旁边有个落脚点 感觉一下 当你准备好

translation.en: and when you're ready, give me your hand, and I'll pull you up.
translation.zh: 感觉一下 当你准备好 把手递给我 然后我拉你上去

translation.en: I can't find it!
translation.zh: 我找不到

translation.en: [Kaylie] Okay, just a little to your right.
translation.zh: 好了 就是右边一点

translation.en: Yes, right there! Come on. [grunts]
translation.zh: 是的 就是那里 来吧 对

translation.en: Are you okay?
translation.zh: 你没事吧？

translation.en: Yeah. I just can't stop thinking
translation.zh: 是的 我就是一直在想要和楚伊一起 做那个按摩

translation.en: about getting a couple's massage with Chewy.
translation.zh: 我就是一直在想要和楚伊一起 做那个按摩

translation.en: Look, we're almost on solid ground! Let's go.
translation.zh: 我们快到硬地上了 走吧

translation.en: Careful. Yeah.
translation.zh: 小心点 好的

translation.en: Okay. Everybody, grab on to this scarf.
translation.zh: 好了 各位 抓住这条围巾

translation.en: But it's my mom's, so don't drop it, or she'll fire me.
translation.zh: 这是我妈的 千万别掉下去 否则她会开除我

translation.en: From the show? From the family.
translation.zh: -从节目开除？ -从家族除名

translation.en: Okay, so we've got to keep going, or we'll never catch the Lumberjacks.
translation.zh: 好了 我们要继续前进 否则赶不上伐木工队

translation.en: Which way do we go?
translation.zh: 我们走哪一边？

translation.en: My compass, it's gone.
translation.zh: 我的指南针不见了

translation.en: Oh, no! It must have fallen out of your pocket when you fell.
translation.zh: 噢 不 肯定是你掉下去时遗失了

translation.en: So let's recap.
translation.zh: 我们回想一下

translation.en: Your shortcut got us lost, which made me lose my compass.
translation.zh: 你的捷径让我们迷路 我的指南针也不见了

translation.en: So now we're going to lose to the Lumberjacks again!
translation.zh: 我们又要再一次输给伐木工队

translation.en: And it's all your fault!
translation.zh: 这都是你的错

translation.en: Amber, wait!
translation.zh: 安博 等等

translation.en: What's the matter with her?
translation.zh: 她怎么回事？

translation.en: She's upset because that was her mom's compass.
translation.zh: 她不开心 因为那是她妈妈的指南针

translation.en: They always used it when they went camping.
translation.zh: 她们去露营时的必备工具

translation.en: But then her mom died last year.
translation.zh: 但是她妈妈去年过世了

translation.en: They were super close, and it's been really hard on her.
translation.zh: 她们感情很好 这对她来说很难

translation.en: Oh, no.
translation.zh: 噢 不

translation.en: Poor Amber. No wonder she's so upset.
translation.zh: 可怜的安博 难怪她这么不开心

translation.en: You guys wait here.
translation.zh: 你们在这里等着

translation.en: I should go too.
translation.zh: 我也要去

translation.en: My shawty needs some sweet X's and O's from her love thug Chewy.
translation.zh: 我的爱人肯定需要来自 楚伊的亲吻和拥抱

translation.en: Hasn't she suffered enough?
translation.zh: 你是不是嫌她不够痛苦？

translation.en: That seat's taken.
translation.zh: 这里有人了

translation.en: Weird. When I made the reservation,
translation.zh: 真奇怪 当我预约的时候 我特别要求

translation.en: I specifically requested this uncomfortable spot on the ground.
translation.zh: 当我预约的时候 我特别要求 地上这个不舒服的位置

translation.en: [laughs] Just kidding.
translation.zh: 开玩笑的

translation.en: I'm a celebrity. I don't need reservations.
translation.zh: 我是个名人 我不需要预约

translation.en: Amber, I am so incredibly sorry about your mom's compass.
translation.zh: 安博 你妈妈指南针的事 我非常抱歉

translation.en: Hey.
translation.zh: 嘿

translation.en: You know what's weird?
translation.zh: 你知道什么很奇怪？

translation.en: This is the first time I haven't been able to hear the freeway in a long time.
translation.zh: 这是我第一次 这么久没听到 高速路的声音

translation.en: It's kind of nice.
translation.zh: 挺不错的

translation.en: Peaceful.
translation.zh: 很平静

translation.en: Don't you think?
translation.zh: 你不觉得吗？

translation.en: I guess.
translation.zh: 大概吧

translation.en: Until a bear comes along. Good thing I can run faster than you.
translation.zh: 如果有熊出没 好事是我跑得比你快

translation.en: That's what you think. I've been outrunning the paparazzi since I was two,
translation.zh: 只是你以为 我两岁开始就要 躲避狗仔队

translation.en: which is not easy in bedazzled booties.
translation.zh: 穿着花哨的鞋子跑得快很难的

translation.en: You know,
translation.zh: 你知道

translation.en: when my mom and I went camping,
translation.zh: 我妈和我去露营时

translation.en: this is how we chose our spot.
translation.zh: 我们就是这样选址的

translation.en: When we couldn't hear the cars anymore.
translation.zh: 直到听不到车声才停下

translation.en: I get that.
translation.zh: 我明白

translation.en: And...
translation.zh: 而且

translation.en: now I get why you like being out in nature so much.
translation.zh: 现在我知道你为什么喜欢呆在野外

translation.en: It's because of your mom, right?
translation.zh: 因为你妈妈 对吗？

translation.en: You know what's dumb?
translation.zh: 你知道什么很傻吗？

translation.en: It's not like it's gonna bring her back.
translation.zh: 并不是说你可以让她回来

translation.en: No, but...
translation.zh: 不是 但是

translation.en: remembering the things that you guys shared,
translation.zh: 记住你们曾分享的一切

translation.en: it helps keep her here.
translation.zh: 就好像她还在

translation.en: And I think she's still here.
translation.zh: 我想就是这样的

translation.en: She would be so proud of you.
translation.zh: 她会为你感到骄傲

translation.en: I don't know why.
translation.zh: 我不知道为什么

translation.en: Are you kidding?
translation.zh: 你开玩笑吗？

translation.en: Look at all the stuff you know! How to read a trail,
translation.zh: 你知道很多事 怎么分辨路线

translation.en: the fact the wilderness cruelly prevents cell phone service.
translation.zh: 荒野残忍地阻挡了手机信号的事实

translation.en: Are you absolutely sure about that one?
translation.zh: 你真的确定这一点吗？

translation.en: I'm sure.
translation.zh: 我确定

translation.en: Plus, you never give up.
translation.zh: 加上 你永不放弃

translation.en: And you're a great leader.
translation.zh: 你是个很棒的领队

translation.en: I just got us lost and put all you kids in danger.
translation.zh: 我让大家迷路 还让孩子们陷入险境

translation.en: Another Kaylie catastrophe, as my mom would say.
translation.zh: 凯莉式的灾难 我妈会这样说

translation.en: What?
translation.zh: 什么？

translation.en: Your mom must be super proud of you.
translation.zh: 你妈肯定很为你自豪

translation.en: Nope. Actually, she just thinks I'm a mess and can't handle anything.
translation.zh: 不会 她只会觉得我一团糟 什么都做不好

translation.en: You are not a mess, and you sure handled everything back on that cliff.
translation.zh: 你不是的 你在悬崖上处理得很好

translation.en: Listen, you stayed calm,
translation.zh: 听着 你很冷静

translation.en: and you saved my life.
translation.zh: 你救了我的命

translation.en: Thanks for that, by the way.
translation.zh: 顺便要说 谢谢你

translation.en: You're welcome.
translation.zh: 不客气

translation.en: So, you mean my mom might actually be... wrong?
translation.zh: 那么 你是说我妈可能是错的吗？

translation.en: Maybe I can handle stuff?
translation.zh: 也许我也能把事情做好？

translation.en: -I do. -[sighs]
translation.zh: 是的

translation.en: And I think the Porcupines could use an adult leader after all.
translation.zh: 豪猪队还是需要一个成年领队

translation.en: Well, co-leader.
translation.zh: 至少是联合领队

translation.en: Okay, something just messed with my hair, and I don't think it was Ray Ray!
translation.zh: 好的 有东西在搞我的头发 我想不是瑞瑞

translation.en: Oh...
translation.zh: 噢

translation.en: I think that's bird poop.
translation.zh: 我想那是鸟粪

translation.en: Oh.
translation.zh: 噢

translation.en: Okay.
translation.zh: 好的

translation.en: Kaylie!
translation.zh: 凯莉

translation.en: A bird just pooped on your head, and you didn't freak out!
translation.zh: 一只鸟在你头顶拉屎 但你没有失控

translation.en: -Told you you can handle anything. -[chuckles]
translation.zh: 我就说你能做得好

translation.en: Well if that's the case, what are we doing just sitting here?
translation.zh: 既然这样 那我们为何还坐着？

translation.en: -We should go beat those Lumberjerks! -Yeah!
translation.zh: -我们该去打败伐木工队 -对啊

translation.en: Oh, but don't you want me to wipe that poop out of your hair first?
translation.zh: 但我是不是该先帮你整理下头发？

translation.en: Yeah, but with what?
translation.zh: 但你用什么？

translation.en: How about your mom's scarf?
translation.zh: 或者你妈的围巾

translation.en: Think I can handle that.
translation.zh: 我想这可以接受

translation.en: Okay.
translation.zh: 好的

translation.en: Thanks, Amber. Let's go.
translation.zh: 谢谢你 安博

translation.en: -The trail is that way! -The trail is that way!
translation.zh: -路线在那边 -路线在那边

translation.en: Finally!
translation.zh: 终于

translation.en: I was starting to get worry wrinkles.
translation.zh: 我都担心得出皱纹了

translation.en: Hey, guys. What'd we miss?
translation.zh: 有什么新闻？

translation.en: Well, Chewy and Valeria are currently trying to trip a caterpillar,
translation.zh: 楚伊和瓦莱莉雅在玩毛毛虫

translation.en: so I'm going to go with nothing.
translation.zh: 所以我什么都不带

translation.en: Are you okay?
translation.zh: 你没事吧？

translation.en: Yeah, but I'd be better if we knew which way to go.
translation.zh: 是的 但如果知道该走哪边就好了

translation.en: We'll never get off this mountain.
translation.zh: 我们没法下山了

translation.en: On the bright side,
translation.zh: 往好处想 凯莉·康纳德的最后自拍

translation.en: Kaylie Konrad's final selfie will be with me!
translation.zh: 往好处想 凯莉·康纳德的最后自拍 将会是和我一起 全世界都会 纪念凯莉和瑞瑞

translation.en: The whole world will mourn Kaylie and Ray Ray.
translation.zh: 将会是和我一起 全世界都会 纪念凯莉和瑞瑞

translation.en: Uh, well, Kaylie anyway.
translation.zh: 应该只有凯莉

translation.en: Aw, Valeria.
translation.zh: 瓦莱莉雅

translation.en: So, you like me now?
translation.zh: 你现在喜欢我了？

translation.en: Duh. Otherwise, you'd have a giant curly hair growing out of your cheek.
translation.zh: 你觉得呢 不然你脸上就会长出 巨大的卷发

translation.en: Okay, you always want the sun in front of you for the best lighting.
translation.zh: 好了 你总是希望太阳在前面 光照充足

translation.en: Don't squint.
translation.zh: 望镜头

translation.en: -Kaylie, that's it! -I know! That's like Selfie 101.
translation.zh: -凯莉 就是这样 -我知道 这是自拍基础知识

translation.en: No, I mean the sun is in front of us, and it sets in the west, right?
translation.zh: 不是 我说太阳在我们前面 在西边落山 对吗？

translation.en: So that way is west!
translation.zh: 所以这边是西边

translation.en: Right! And if Dudley is driving me west on Wilshire,
translation.zh: 对的 如果达利开车送我 往西去威尔希尔

translation.en: then we turn right to go to Burke Williams!
translation.zh: 对的 如果达利开车送我 往西去威尔希尔 然后右转去伯克·威廉姆斯

translation.en: That's where I got our Groupon!
translation.zh: 那就是我买按摩套票的地方

translation.en: So north must be that way!
translation.zh: 那北面肯定是这边

translation.en: Which means we need to go that way to get to Sunset Peak!
translation.zh: 我们走这边才能去日落峰

translation.en: Which is right here!
translation.zh: 也就是这里

translation.en: That's not Sunset Peak. That's Selena Gomez's house.
translation.zh: 那不是日落峰 是赛琳娜·戈麦斯的房子

translation.en: Oh, right.
translation.zh: 噢 对的

translation.en: Which is also smaller than my house. Yay!
translation.zh: 这也比我的房子小

translation.en: Again!
translation.zh: 又来了

translation.en: I... hate... hiking.
translation.zh: 我 讨厌 徒步

translation.en: On the bright side, my calves are going to look amazing.
translation.zh: 乐观点想 我的小腿会变得很棒

translation.en: I could have flown to the peak by now.
translation.zh: 我本来该飞到山顶了

translation.en: But, "No," you said. "Leave your broom at home," you said.
translation.zh: 但是 你说 把扫帚留在家里

translation.en: We're almost at the top!
translation.zh: 我们快到顶了

translation.en: I hope we beat the Lumberjacks!
translation.zh: 希望我们能打败伐木工队

translation.en: Hey, Porcupoops!
translation.zh: 嘿 豪猪队

translation.en: So what took you so long?
translation.zh: 你们这么久的？

translation.en: I was visiting your mom in prison.
translation.zh: 我去监狱看望你妈了

translation.en: She was framed!
translation.zh: 她被陷害了

translation.en: That was mean.
translation.zh: 你真恶毒

translation.en: I am so sorry. I had no idea she was really in prison.
translation.zh: 我很抱歉 我不知道她真的在监狱

translation.en: She's not. Psych!
translation.zh: 她没有 开玩笑的

translation.en: -[all laugh] -Got 'em.
translation.zh: 你们上当了

translation.en: You're so funny.
translation.zh: 你真搞笑

translation.en: Hey, you made it. Great job.
translation.zh: 嘿 你们做到了 做得好

translation.en: That was a tough hike. All the other teams gave up.
translation.zh: 这是非常辛苦的徒步 其他队伍都放弃了

translation.en: Well, not us.
translation.zh: 我们没有

translation.en: Right. 'Cause when the going gets tough...
translation.zh: 对的 因为当事情变得艰难

translation.en: I call my publicist!
translation.zh: 我带电话给我的公关

translation.en: Therapist?
translation.zh: 治疗师？

translation.en: Life coach?
translation.zh: 人生导师？

translation.en: Can someone give me a hint?
translation.zh: 你们能给点提示吗？

translation.en: Yeah, dump these chumps. They are not on your level.
translation.zh: 抛弃这些笨蛋吧 他们跟你不同档次

translation.en: Why are they walking like my nana when her bunions act up?
translation.zh: 他们走路怎么像我奶奶 拇囊炎发作的样子？

translation.en: Oh, they all got these wicked blisters. Like, out of nowhere.
translation.zh: 他们都起了可怕的水泡 不知道为什么

translation.en: Way to go, Valeria.
translation.zh: 做得好 瓦莱莉雅

translation.en: Remind me never to cross you.
translation.zh: 提醒我别得罪你

translation.en: The blisters are just the beginning. Wait 'til they go home and try to pee.
translation.zh: 水泡只是开始 等他们回家尿尿就知道了

translation.en: Hey, Kaylie, you thirsty?
translation.zh: 嘿 凯莉 你口渴吗？

translation.en: You wish.
translation.zh: 你想多了

translation.en: Sure.
translation.zh: 当然

translation.en: Thanks.
translation.zh: 谢谢

translation.en: Well, we should probably head back down before we lose the light.
translation.zh: 在天黑之前我们该下山了

translation.en: We'll be right behind you.
translation.zh: 我们会跟在后面

translation.en: I'm sick of being behind them.
translation.zh: 我厌倦了跟在他们后面

translation.en: I don't mind the view.
translation.zh: 我不介意看风景

translation.en: We'll get 'em next time.
translation.zh: 下次我们会赢的

translation.en: We have a whole year to win that Wilderness Trophy.
translation.zh: 我们有一整年可以赢荒野奖杯

translation.en: Absolutely.
translation.zh: 肯定的

translation.en: And now that we're a team, there's nothing we can't do.
translation.zh: 我们是一个团队 没有做不到的事

translation.en: No challenge we can't face together.
translation.zh: 没有不能面对的挑战

translation.en: Yeah!
translation.zh: 对啊

translation.en: You know what? You're right. But first, we have to get back down the mountain.
translation.zh: 你说得对 但是 首先我们要下山

translation.en: Right. Okay, so where's the escalator?
translation.zh: 对的 自动扶梯在哪里？

translation.en: It's right over there next to the gift shop.
translation.zh: 就在那边 在礼品店旁边

translation.en: Ooh, shopping!
translation.zh: 噢 礼品店！

translation.en: I hope they take Kaylies!
translation.zh: 希望他们肯收凯莉币

translation.en: ♪ Ay, ay, Team Kaylie ♪
translation.zh: 哎 哎 凯莉小分队
